description: Hi there! I am a Software Engineer primarily focusing on Web Development for a small company in the Pacific Northwest.
I always keep learning; whether it is a new web framework, a new programming language, or diving close to the hardware, I have an insatiable curiosity.

bullets.point: B.S. in Computer Science from Oregon State University
Currently working as a Software Engineer in Tualatin, OR since September 2020
Two years of programming experiences as a Student Analyst / Programmer for Oregon State University
Strong skills in object oriented programming and web development (Java, JavaScript and HTML/CSS)
Desire to learn, grow and contribute

description: I want to learn from the best software engineers to deliver high quality software to end users. I enjoy growing my skill set using both old and new technologies, solving challenging problems across the software stack. Best of all, I want to contribute to new and existing work by bringing a humble perspective, curiosity, and friendliness.
